name: Collage Doll #001 "Pia"
description:
Collage Doll #001 "Pia" comes from an exotic place. She has the ability to talk to nature, and for her, plants have a talking mask. But according to the folklore, it is actually the bird hat on her head that talks with the plants.

Collage Dolls is a series that is generated through self-experimentation.
